{"tid":429221,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人搭過阿聯猶","createTime":"2017-10-08T16:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T03:16:57.000Z","uid":79502,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"bd3d04acc664269b11037239d55b6c98cd158b82","tid":429221,"uid":79502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:39:16.000Z","msg":"如題"},{"pid":"3c5a37cf1ba9612eb4374dec4d93beaea65829a0","tid":429221,"uid":6604,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T16:40:40.000Z","msg":"坐過阿聯酋<br />\n未坐過阿聯猶"},{"pid":"dc99cd4a9e43b7a8f1da93a3b71af8b80d80d8ce","tid":429221,"uid":70733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:13:42.000Z","msg":"d機唔錯"},{"pid":"601d833bd6b80787204b3dfe7caf49ddafcdf9bf","tid":429221,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T18:15:27.000Z","msg":"幾好"},{"pid":"822551bb5dccd86871b2d7df271bd411484471a6","tid":429221,"uid":50894,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T01:45:01.000Z","msg":"D 野勁好食 以飛機餐黎計"},{"pid":"5c008eb9766ee5d63ab497a809c89dcf56b0a909","tid":429221,"uid":13035,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T02:29:16.000Z","msg":"機幾舒服<br />\n但d staff係我見過咁多間之中最西<br />\n唔知係咪我咁唔好彩"},{"pid":"b51474b4c4118c5d113fbea7e2d31432f1f1e871","tid":429221,"uid":6604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:18:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機幾舒服<br />\n但d staff係我見過咁多間之中最西<br />\n唔知係咪我咁唔好彩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n空姐/空少鍾意 count 下佢應該 serve 幾多客<br />\n係50個就50個<br />\n即使第51個坐喺隔離<br />\n佢地都唔會幫佢拎走個 tray<br />\n<br />\n派餐手腳慢<br />\n坐去 BKK <br />\n差唔多用左成程機先做完個 meal service <br />\n(呢方便CX就真係快手)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除此之外，其他嘢都唔錯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2435fde11e06dff1320aa63d82de35ecfae100e2","tid":429221,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:26:05.000Z","msg":"坐過好多次都幾好<br />\n每次都準時<br />\n<br />\n最驚險一次係杜拜沙塵暴<br />\n要急降係個叫Al Ain既沙漠到<br />\n結果係沙漠等左四粒鐘先飛番杜拜<br />\n<br />\n除左個次都無問題"},{"pid":"8035dee69c825e9baf2a84978be82e669950405c","tid":429221,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:30:59.000Z","msg":"坐過一次 真心唔錯"},{"pid":"6949f6d3a2cf7b667a8d343177b507a9f36b862c","tid":429221,"uid":345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:34:56.000Z","msg":"Staff西咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我搭果幾次都唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd05c1d370e5c07b305fa47a211539ae37a19e80","tid":429221,"uid":59140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T03:49:09.000Z","msg":"兩年前坐去羅馬 A380+777<br />\n有wifi<br />\n飛機餐無豬<br />\n座位大致舒服<br />\n不過係A380遇到氣流就郁動比較大<br />\n空姐空少都幾有禮貌<br />\n整體大致上都無乜大問題"},{"pid":"7ea475de87129f321531edb4dec74d42e830cfdb","tid":429221,"uid":12490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:12:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>坐過好多次都幾好<br />\n每次都準時<br />\n<br />\n最驚險一次係杜拜沙塵暴<br />\n要急降係個叫Al Ain既沙漠到<br />\n結果係沙漠等左四粒鐘先飛番杜拜<br />\n<br />\n除左個次都無問題</blockquote><br />\n咁沙塵暴都唔關阿聯酋事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7134f548c22af0488e6ca010dba14c19385709c9","tid":429221,"uid":90716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:23:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>坐過好多次都幾好<br />\n每次都準時<br />\n<br />\n最驚險一次係杜拜沙塵暴<br />\n要急降係個叫Al Ain既沙漠到<br />\n結果係沙漠等左四粒鐘先飛番杜拜<br />\n<br />\n除左個次都無問題</blockquote><br />\n咁沙塵暴都唔關阿聯酋事嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我只係係杜拜轉機 <br />\n咁係沙漠四個鐘就導致我miss左下一班機<br />\n不過都係阿聯酋既 所以就安排左我坐下一班機"},{"pid":"b21b498314cc80d208d22b5ed998906cacd3d088","tid":429221,"uid":51981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T04:23:44.000Z","msg":"覺得好過cx"},{"pid":"0429cb48e8dea38b7432f4712fc76bdafd8f23a1"